 7. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
