.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, coral, black, ebony
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person who likes ebony##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person who likes coral##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who likes black##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who likes coral##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Color         | white | black  | ebony     | coral  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, satire, zombie, mystery
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, german, italian
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the italian##1
 2. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 3. the person drinking sprite is the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person watching mystery movies##5
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the german##3
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the person watching zombie movies is not the brazilian##6
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the italian is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the person watching mystery movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
14. the brazilian is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola      | sprite  | soy-milk | juice        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | chess   | baking   | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | satire   | zombie    | crime      |
| Nationality   | british   | italian | german   | brazilian    |

