.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, red, orange, chestnut
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, puzzles, rock-climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, fisherman, photographer, project-manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, roller, subway
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person who likes orange##6
 2. the dancer is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the dancer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 5. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
 6. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
 8. the person who likes emerald is not to the left of the photographer##8
 9. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the person who likes red is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the project-manager##7
11. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Color    | orange        | red        | emerald        | chestnut   |
| Hobby       | card-games      | camping      | rock-climbing | puzzles |
| Job         | project-manager | photographer | fisherman     | dancer  |
| Transport   | roller          | jet-ski      | quad-bike     | subway  |

